bgp4PathAttrBest OBJECT-TYPE SYNTAX INTEGER { false(1),-- not chosen as best route true(2) -- chosen as best route } MAX-ACCESS read-only STATUS deprecated DESCRIPTION "An indication of whether this route was chosen as the best BGP4 route for this destination.
